thread.title: Tony Rice

author: Tony Rice
title: Tony Rice
text:
Dear Janet
I wanted to thank you for your assistance in my recent transfer of funds to the UK. The complete transaction was smooth and trouble free from my point of view due entirely to your help, understanding and professionalism. I was very impressed with you personally and Torfx in general.
Thanks again and I will not hesitate to use your services again in the future.
